com.snda.storage.service.multi.cs

Class CSServiceEventAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snda.storage.service.multi.StorageServiceEventAdaptor
      • com.snda.storage.service.multi.cs.CSServiceEventAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CSServiceEventListener, StorageServiceEventListener

    public class CSServiceEventAdaptor
extends StorageServiceEventAdaptor
implements CSServiceEventListener
    Simple implementation of CSServiceEventListener to listen for events produced by ThreadedCSService and ThreadedStorageService.

    By default this adaptor does nothing but store the first Error event it comes across, if any, and make it available through StorageServiceEventAdaptor.getErrorThrown().

    The behaviour of this class can be specialised by over-riding the appropriate event methods, though always be sure to call the super version of these methods if you are relying on the default error-trapping functions of this class.
